# Scaffold templates: markdown carries {{handle}}/{{rosterTable}}/{{channel}} tokens
# (and a {{handle}}.md path-token file) that `anthill init` renders verbatim.
# Prettier must NOT reflow these — the rendered docs/team output must stay byte-identical.
templates/

# Project knowledge docs — prose/pheromone (backlog, sessions, lessons, fragments,
# projects, architecture, …). Prettier's markdown parser mangles prose: a line that
# starts with `+`/`-`/`*` (which hand-wrapping can accidentally produce) becomes a
# stray list bullet, and there's no prettier setting to disable that. Hit live
# 2026-06-30. Same principle anthill's own bootstrap/upgrade apply to a consumer's
# `.anthill/` footprint — the knowledge docs are load-bearing; keep the formatter off them.
docs/

